body:
( scenarios )

[ Takes place during Inifinity War ]

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

Y/n: You four! Come quick, something’s going on outside.

Stephen: I’m sorry, who is she again?

Tony: Just one of the many ex- villains that we saved from the darkness. Oh and, an ex fling of a friend. Come on!

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

Peter turns around seeing Y/n fly into the air towards the space ship, only for her to be thrown back by a force seconds later.

Peter: Hey Ned, I need you to cause a distraction!

Ned:

Ned: Oh shit, there’s that new hero! She’s kinda hot.. Hey, how old do you think she is?

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

Peter saving you, to then only regret it..

Y/n: Thanks for that, Parker, but I had it all under control.

Peter: Well it didn’t seem like you did. You’re lucky I even showed up.

Y/n: You shouldn’t go. It’s dangerous for a little freshmen like you to be there!

Peter: You know what? I was actually quite terrified of what might happen once I get there, but now I think I just have more motivation to kick some ass. Ugh, you’re so -

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

Y/n trying to look out for Peter -

Y/n looked behind her to see how high she’s gone up.

Y/n: Peter! What are you doing here?

Peter: I’m here to help save the world *grunt* obviously!

Before Peter could reach her, Y/n was quick to kick him harshly, sending him falling right back down.

Peter: WHAT WAS THAT FOR?!

Y/n: Sorry Spidey, Iron Man’s orders! We can’t have a teenager’s life in our hands.

Peter: STOP ACTING LIKE I’M THE ONLY YOUNG HERO HERE! YOU’RE ONLY OLDER BY A YEAR!

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

Peter trying to give reasons to dislike Y/n -

Peter: You shouldn’t trust her, she’ll only break your heart in unfortunate ways. And she was once one of the bad guys so -

Stephen: You’re the one who had the fling.

Peter: What? How’d you know that?

Stephen: Your metal friend over there.

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

Saving Y/n Pt .2 -

Thanos throws you a big hit sending you flying to the air.

Y/n: PLEASE LAND ON SOMETHING SOFT PLEASE LAND ON SOMETHING SOFT PLEASE LAND ON SOMETHING SOFT

Peter: Y/n! I’m on my way!

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

The Vanishing -

Peter: Y/n

Y/n: Oh Peter…

Tony: You’ll be alright, kid.

┝━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┥

ᴴᵒʷ ᵃᵇᵒᵘᵗ ᵃ ᴾᵗ. ²?

80+ ❤️’s = Endgame version will be made

summary: tom x reader where they’ve been dating since filming for civil war, and they just told all of them while taking a lunch break...
question: tom x reader where they’ve been dating since filming for civil war, and they just told all of them while taking a lunch break from filming endgame. everyone was so happy! (insert some protective ‘brothers’ for c evans, mackie and seb, a very happy zoe and lizzie and robert just calling for a celebration!) thank you <33
answer:
Oh my god, I love this!


Requests are open!

The director yelled cut, and you snapped out of it, breaking out of your character with a smile on your face after a really good take. It was your last week filming End Game and the entire cast was on set every day. Including Tom, your boyfriend for the last few years that you managed to keep under wraps.

You broke for lunch and headed over towards the craft service table, already seeing Tom stuffing his face alongnside Sebastian and Mackie. He smiled up at you proudly, handing you a water bottle as he walked over to you.

“You nailed that scene,” Tom told you with excitement. He always watched you work whenever he could, and was always blown away by your hard work in efforts, “God, I love you so much, y/n,” he said a little too loud.

You stared at him widely, letting out a cough as you noticed heads turning towards you after Tom’s comment. The two of you managed to keep your relationship a secret for professional reasons, and were planning on going public once you finished filming End Game together.

“Did he just say what I think he just said?” Sebastian asked, looking at the two of you in an attempt not to laugh.

Tom didn’t even realize what he had said, he was way too busy complimenting you and lost in his own world, “What’re you talking about, man?” He asked Seb.

“Guys, come on! Let them be!” Zoe exclaimed from her chair, shaking her head at all of the silliness.

“Holland and y/n are dating! I knew it!” Mackie shouted with a loud laugh. He ran over to the two of you, clunking your heads together jokingly, “You are auch a cute couple,” Mackie teased you both.

Sebastian joined in on the teasing, calling the rest of the cast over to shout and clap. You watched as Tom’s face grew beet red, matching yours as your buried his face in his shoulders.

“Sorry..” Tom cringed out an apology to you. But you weren’t mad. You thought it was sort of cute how embarrassed he was getting after shouting his affection towards you, “Can we stop now?” Tom asked Mackie and Seb as they gathered everyone else over.

“You better not do anything stupid to mess this up,” Evans laughed out as he gave you a protective hug, making you roll your eyes at all of them.

Tom scoffed, “Y/n and I have been together since Civl War, I haven’t yet!” He shouted proudly, taking your hand in his.

“Can we get Downey on the phone? I don’t think he knows yet,” Mackie said to Seb as they pulled out their phones, continuing to tease you two.

You kissed Tom’s cheek, trying to make him feel any less embarrassed. You were proud to have him as your boyfriend, and even more happy now thay it was no longer a secret. As Tom squeezed your hand, you could tell he was just was relieved.

The suit here

♕ A crown will not complete you or make you happy. It is simply part of the uniform of an elite group of people who are just trying to make the world a better place ♕

Staci Rothwell wasn’t normal in any sense of the word. She wasn’t considered a normal teenager due to her powers yet she wasn’t considered normal in the superhero realm either due to once again her powers. But she was perfectly content with the way her life was. 

She was living basically on her own, her father coming and going on occasion, and she was fine being by herself and doing her own thing keeping her little rural town in Ohio safe. But all that was turned upside down when Tony Stark showed up at her doorstep asking for her help to fight against a deranged Captain America. 

 After the battle, Tony proceeded to take her under his wing very much to her dismay. He bought her an apartment in Queens right next door to Peter Parker’s so it was easier to keep an eye on both of them.  It was difficult adjusting to both her new living situation and with the many powers, she was still developing and struggling to control.

summary: What my dream is for the Far From Home End-Credits Gag...
title: What my dream is for the Far From Home End-Credits Gag...
body:
[We open on the first day of class for Peter’s…senior year? Junior year? Who knows… Peter and Ned walk into their AP Chem class together. Ned calmly takes his seat, but Peter freezes in place, wide-eyed. 

Standing at the board, struggling with a regular Expo marker that is too small for his hand, the teacher is writing “Mr. Banner.” He turns, satisfied. He locks eyes with Peter. The two freeze.] 

HULK: [grinning as he recognizes Peter] Heyyy…!

PETER: (clears throat) NOPE. NO—

HULK: You’re that little bug guy, right?

PETER: [growing red-faced and very uncomfortable, making slashing motions across his throat rapidly] Please don’t. Just…

HULK: Bug-Man? Is that right? The Bugling?

PETER: PLEASE STOP TALKING.
